# 7. Self-exploratory

Combine reference line (in section 6.4), interactive sparkline (in section 6.5) with sales_data datatable (in section 5.4).


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-fold="true" code-summary="Show code"}
reactable(
  sales_data,
  defaultPageSize = 13,
  columns = list(
    Product = colDef(maxWidth = 200),
    `Monthly Sales` = colDef(
      cell = react_sparkline(
        sales_data,
        highlight_points = highlight_points(
          min = "red", max = "skyblue"),
        line_width = 1,
        statline = "mean",
        bandline = "innerquartiles",
        bandline_color = "green"
        ))
  )
)
```

